<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">
  Your RezumFit subscription has been cancelled. We're sorry to see you go!
</p>

<div style="margin: 24px 0; padding: 16px; background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #fbbf24; border-radius: 8px;">
  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #92400e; font-weight: 600;">What happens next?</p>
  <p style="margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #92400e;">
    <% if @subscription.current_period_end && @subscription.current_period_end > Time.current %>
      You'll continue to have Pro access until <strong><%= @subscription.current_period_end.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></strong>. After that, your account will revert to the free plan with pay-per-use credits.
    <% else %>
      Your account has been reverted to the free plan. You can still use RezumFit with pay-per-use credits.
    <% end %>
  </p>
</div>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">
  You can resubscribe anytime to get unlimited access again.
</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0 16px;">
  <a href="<%= new_subscription_url %>" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed); color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block;">
    Resubscribe
  </a>
</div>

<p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 24px;">
  If you cancelled by mistake or have any questions, reply to this email and we'll help sort things out.
</p>
